high_descs: Turn around and face the counter.
Pick up the bowl to the right of the sink.
Move to the left to the sink.
Fill the bowl with water.
Go to the microwave on the other side of the kitchen.
Put the bowl of water in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl of water in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around to the counter directly behind you.
Pick up the bowl on the right side of the counter.
Take the bowl and take a step over to the left towards the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink, turn the water on and then off. Pick up the bowl from the sink.
Take the bowl and turn around. Go around the island to the far side of the kitchen and find the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the bowl inside, then shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Wash a bowl and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the left, take a step, then turn to the left and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the bowl sitting on the counter.
Turn to the left, take a step, then turn right to face the sink
Put the bowl in the sink, run water, remove the bowl from the sink.
Turn to the right, take a step, then turn right and walk across the room, then turn right and walk across the room, then turn left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the bowl in the microwave, then shut the microwave.
anns.task_desc: TO wash a bowl, as well as store it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter.
Pick up the bowl.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Fill the bowl with water.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Put the bowl in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl of water in the microwave.
